quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  68,43,"KhashiAAatan absaruhumtarhaquhum thillatun waqad kanoo yudAAawna ilaassujoodi wahum salimoon"
  68,44,"Fatharnee waman yukaththibubihatha alhadeethi sanastadrijuhum min haythula yaAAlamoon"
  68,45,"Waomlee lahum inna kaydee mateen"
  68,46,"Am tas-aluhum ajran fahum min maghraminmuthqaloon"
  68,47,"Am AAindahumu alghaybu fahum yaktuboon"
  68,48,"Fasbir lihukmi rabbikawala takun kasahibi alhooti ith nadawahuwa makthoom"
  68,49,"Lawla an tadarakahu niAAmatunmin rabbihi lanubitha bilAAara-i wahuwa mathmoom"
  68,50,"Fajtabahu rabbuhu fajaAAalahumina assaliheen"
  68,51,"Wa-in yakadu allatheenakafaroo layuzliqoonaka bi-absarihim lamma samiAAooaththikra wayaqooloona innahu lamajnoon"
  68,52,"Wama huwa illa thikrunlilAAalameen"
  69,1,"Alhaqqa"
  69,2,"Ma alhaqqa"
  69,3,"Wama adraka ma alhaqqa"
  69,4,"Kaththabat thamoodu waAAadun bilqariAAa"
  69,5,"Faamma thamoodu faohlikoo bittaghiya"
  69,6,"Waamma AAadun faohlikoo bireehinsarsarin AAatiya"
  69,7,"Sakhkharaha AAalayhim sabAAa layalinwathamaniyata ayyamin husooman fataraalqawma feeha sarAAa kaannahum aAAjazunakhlin khawiya"
  69,8,"Fahal tara lahum min baqiya"
